Package org.grapheditor.editor.exporters

The classes in this package are used to export the graph to externial file formats.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
EPSExporter Objects of this class is used to export graphs to a an EPS-image.
EPSExporterVisual This class purpose is to make it easy to show a dialog that lets the user deside a eps-file to export the an eps-image to.
MathematicaExporter Objects of this class is used to export graphs to a file format that is possible to import to Mathematica.
MathematicaExporterVisual This class has a method that provides an visual interface to select a Mathematica importable file to save to.
NeighbourListExporter The neighbor list exporter exports file to the same file format as the Mathematica exporter with the differense that it doesnt have the to numbers that represents tha position for each vertex.
NeighbourListExporterVisual This class has a method that displayes an interface that the user can use to select a file to export a neigbour list to.
 

Package org.grapheditor.editor.exporters Description

The classes in this package are used to export the graph to externial file formats.
